node.text: Thank you @indeskribeabull I was needing this, this morning. I had to follow you. I had this same conversation with my 11 year old last night but she put it better so I made him watch this. It’s better to be consistently good than occasionally great! Also right now I’m watching a couple ppl around me thinking their shortcuts to wealth, power, success, happiness etc will help them win. “If you’re not a reliable servant he will pass you up every time.” #aintnoplug #youtheplug #tenacity #consistency #noshortcuts
